---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About - The Lead Letter" description="About EntrLabs - The Lead Letter, a weekly publication on leadership, service, work, learning, and better judgment.">
  <article class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="kicker">The Publication</p>
      <h1>Weekly Updates</h1>
      <div class="rule-double slim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p class="lede">
        EntrLabs - The Lead Letter is a weekly publication for people who lead, build, teach,
        advise, manage, and serve. Each issue turns current signals into practical questions
        about judgment, responsibility, work, learning, and helping people rise.
      </p>
      <p>
        Published by <a href="https://entr.cc/entrlabs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EntrLabs</a>,
        the research lab of <a href="https://entr.cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ENTR</a>,
        this work carries leadership research, learning science, and organizational thinking into
        public use: one idea, one practice, one better decision at a time.
      </p>
      <p>
        The publication is written by
        <a href="https://josephiesue.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Joseph E. Iesue</a>,
        a leadership researcher and practitioner. His work in Service Leadership, String Leadership,
        and ELEM informs the way each issue connects ideas to responsibility in the real world.
      </p>
      <p>
        For career pathway work, education-to-profession thinking, and the discipline of forging
        your own path, follow <a href="https://hyoh.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HYOH Career Compass</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="end-mark"><span>Strength Through Service</span></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
